TERMINALIA (
Fig. 3
). Right epandrial lamella black, except for dusky yellow base. Cerci fused with pale brown digitiform tip, a strong bristle below middle (
Fig. 3B
). Left surstylus black, narrow with a truncate tip bearing yellow hairs, dorsal margin with a very long seta at base and a few strong setae near middle (
Fig. 3C
).
